(14, 'surenna-a-unique-luxury-residential-development-in-tulum', 'Surenna: a unique luxury residential development in Tulum', 3, '2a-650x366_fsMOxawy.png', '\"<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>The house of your dreams amid the Mayan jungle<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">For some decades now, Tulum has been one of Mexico&rsquo;s favourite beach destinations because of its historical heritage, its magical jungles and it&rsquo;s beach sunsets, and this has led to its rapid growth. Boutique hotels, resorts, apartments and residential developments have settled in Tulum over the past few years, turning what was once a town into <\\/span><strong>one of the world&rsquo;s most exclusive, trendy and luxurious spots <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">for the summer.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle wp-image-2338\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/01\\/2a-650x366.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"348\\\" height=\\\"196\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Interior render &ndash; Surenna, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle wp-image-2339\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/01\\/2b-650x366.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"348\\\" height=\\\"196\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Room model render &ndash; Surenna, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/surenna.mx\\\">Surenna<\\/a> is the answer for those seeking a place to live in Tulum. This luxury residential development consists of<\\/span><strong> 59 properties starting from 250 m2<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> with large landscapes and lush gardens designed to indulge nature. Amongst the properties, it counts with <\\/span><strong>25 luxury houses of 3 and 4 bedrooms<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, with private pools, terraces and parking. The houses start from 4,368,000 MXN and the lots from 831,600 MXN, with <\\/span><strong>direct financing for up to 24 months<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2340 ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/01\\/3-1-650x366.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"366\\\" \\/> Outdoor Terrace &ndash; Surenna, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/surenna.mx\\\">Surenna<\\/a> has the<\\/span><strong> perfect location<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">: it is just a few minutes away from the main avenues, attractions and beaches of Tulum. In spite of being in a great central location, <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/surenna.mx\\\">Surenna<\\/a> has the advantage of being surrounded by the peace and the magic of the Mayan jungle, as it is in a quiet and calm neighbourhood, away from the noises of the city.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2341 ui-sortable-handle\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/01\\/4-2-650x363.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"363\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Location &ndash; Surenna, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>3 reasons why you should invest in Surenna<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Sometimes, it may seem hard to recognize when an investment opportunity is <\\/span><em><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">really<\\/span><\\/em><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> a good one. Next, we&rsquo;ll tell you three reasons why investing in Surenna is the right choice and one of the best options in the market.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2342 ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/01\\/5-1-650x366.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"366\\\" \\/> Model C House render &ndash; Surenna, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">First of all, it is essential to know that Tulum is divided into regions, according to the quality of its land. This quality then determines the land use and occupation coefficient, and sets the parameters and restrictions for the constructions and developments that will be carried out on those zones. Said that, Surenna is located north of the Gypsea Market, on Region 11, which has a <\\/span><strong>H4 classification<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> for the density of its soil, the best available, allowing a high-quality development with fewer restrictions and higher land use and occupation coefficient. This makes Surenna an excellent investment opportunity, as it is located in a zone with <\\/span><strong>great development projections<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, guaranteeing great returns in the next few years.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2343 ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/01\\/6-650x433.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"433\\\" \\/> Aerial view &ndash; Surenna, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Secondly, Region 11 is a new zone that has still a lot of room for future developments, meaning that all the developments that are already constructed are brand new high-end developments that are still surrounded by the magical Mayan jungle. For this reason, the price of the square meter is one of the lowests of Tulum, as it only costs 165 USD. Resuming: new zone with luxury developments surrounded by nature, in the highest soil-quality region of Tulum, with one of the <\\/span><strong>lowest square-meter prices.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Lastly, Tulum&rsquo;s <\\/span><strong>Partial Development Plan <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">has projected to build soon a <\\/span><strong>dual road access <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">through the North-end of the 5th Avenue. This access will improve the connection and the infrastructure quality of the area, and therefore, of Surenna, adding value to its properties.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Contact us<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 14pt;\\\">If you want to know more about this development, leave your contact information below:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-01-15 10:29:20', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(15, 'nativus-a-unique-glamping-proposal-in-tulum', 'Nativus, a unique glamping proposal in Tulum', 3, 'aerea-400x534_mukCrzlM.jpg', '\"<p><img class=\\\"wp-image-2368 size-medium\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/aerea-400x534.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"225\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Aerial view of Nativus,. Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The glamping phenomenon has reached Tulum, and we think there is no better place to embody it. In the heart of the Mayan Riviera, surrounded by the jungle`s wildlife and amazing ancient archaeological ruins, just a few minutes away from the famous Caribbean beaches sits Nativus, a resting experience that no hotel can match.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Glamping is short for glamorous camping and in Nativus we take this concept to the next level by combining the finest facilities with eco-friendly standards to ensure and maximize our guests well-being and comfort.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Sustainability, our trademark<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><strong><img class=\\\"alignright wp-image-2370 size-medium\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/bathroom-min-400x267.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/strong><img class=\\\"wp-image-2371 size-medium\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/bedroom-min-400x267.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/> Nativu&rsquo;s premium tents &amp; bathrooms from the inside. Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Each of our luxurious and sustainable tents are furnished with king-sized beds and fully equipped bathrooms with open air showers, which are treated with premium housekeeping services in compliance to the actual world-known sanitizing protocols. Moreover, our guests have access to our exclusive docks and natural cenotes, while also benefiting from a delicious and complimentary breakfast.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-2372\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/kayak-min-400x299.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"224\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Kayaking at the cenote. Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Our many services include yoga &amp; sound healing sessions that combined with the splendor of the jungle-like surroundings, make an ideal experience for reaching your inner-peace. We also offer bike rentals to explore the wonders of the local wilderness and lend our guests kayak, paddleboard and snorkeling gear to enjoy the crystal clear waters of the cenotes.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-2369\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/Bar-400x267.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/> Bar &amp; common areas, Tulum, M&eacute;xico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you fancy a relaxing vacation that combines adventure and luxury, all in a remarkable sustainable facility, the glamping experience of Nativus in Tulum is just what you need!<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-03-03 10:33:12', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(16, 'aruna-condominios-de-lujo-en-la-zona-de-mayor-crecimiento-de-tulum', 'Aruna: Condominios de Lujo en la zona de mayor crecimiento de Tulum', 3, '02-FACHADA-LATERAL-ARUNA-650x434_NWFBMctU.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2378\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/02-FACHADA-LATERAL-ARUNA-650x434.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"434\\\" \\/> Vista frontal del complejo Aruna. Tulum, M&eacute;xico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Dise&ntilde;ado por H. Ponce Arquitectos, la simbiosis entre los espacios interiores y exteriores es el rasgo m&aacute;s distintivo que posee Aruna. Dentro del complejo, los espacios se expanden y conectan con las zonas exteriores y adquieren una relaci&oacute;n especial con los espacios naturales, provenientes de la c&eacute;lebre Selva Maya.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">El dise&ntilde;o de Aruna se beneficia de las ventajas de la arquitectura funcional, que siempre tiene en mente las necesidades del usuario, otorg&aacute;ndoles una gran sensaci&oacute;n de confort y bienestar.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2379\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/02-REC&Aacute;MARA-ARUNA-650x591.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"591\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Habitaciones, cocina y comedor de las unidades. Tulum, M&eacute;xico.<img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2377\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/02-DEPARTAMENTO-B-ARUNA-650x562.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"562\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Habitaciones, cocina y comedor de las unidades. Tulum, M&eacute;xico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Estos departamentos bohemios fueron pensados para transmitir paz e intimidad a sus usuarios, trayendoles tranquilidad a sus vidas. Los espacios amplios y la abundante luz solar son unos de los mejores tesoros que posee Aruna. Asimismo, los atardeceres que se pueden presenciar desde all&iacute; hacen valer cada centavo de la inversi&oacute;n .<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Ubicaci&oacute;n:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Aruna yace en un lugar privilegiado, en medio de la Selva Maya y muy cerca de las playas m&aacute;s paradis&iacute;acas de M&eacute;xico y el Mar Caribe, que lo convierten en una residencia &uacute;nica para habitar.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Composici&oacute;n:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Aruna se compone de 29 condominios distribuidos en 3 pisos y de hasta 3 dise&ntilde;os diferentes: Suria (2 habitaciones), Kali (1 habitaci&oacute;n) &amp; Tara (estudio\\/oficina), con la posibilidad de a&ntilde;adir 1 pent-house en cada uno de ellos. <\\/span><strong>El tama&ntilde;o de las unidades var&iacute;a entre 45.93 m2 a 271 m2 y sus precios van desde los U<\\/strong><strong>$S125,000<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. <\\/span><strong>Todas las unidades est&aacute;n listas para entregar con papeles y escritura, y poseen un r&eacute;gimen en condominio<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Hasta el momento, <\\/span><strong>70% de las unidades ya est&aacute;n vendidas, e incluso se encuentra disponible la opci&oacute;n de adquirir una propiedad que se entrega con llave en mano, es decir ya<\\/strong><strong> amobladas<\\/strong><strong> y listas para habitar (&iexcl;o rentar!).<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Cada unidad est&aacute; equipada con calentadores de agua el&eacute;ctricos, aire acondicionado, horno el&eacute;ctrico con hornalla de 4 bocas, ventiladores de bronce y lavabos flotantes con bordes pulidos.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"size-large wp-image-2380\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/03\\/02-ROOF-DEPARTAMENTO-A1-ARUNA-650x464.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"464\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Espacios comunes y exteriores. Tulum, M&eacute;xico.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A su vez, los inquilinos pueden disfrutar de una serie de espacios comunes, como la pileta en la terraza, el pabell&oacute;n de yoga &amp; meditaci&oacute;n, la cabina de masajes, un sal&oacute;n de conferencias, acceso a un club de playa exclusivo y portabicicletas.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">El complejo cuenta con seguridad las 24 horas del d&iacute;a, Wi-Fi en &aacute;reas comunes, acceso controlado al predio y muchos espacios verdes.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Invertir en Aruna:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Advirtiendo el crecimiento inminente de la zona donde est&aacute; ubicada Aruna, consideramos que este es un proyecto muy atractivo para comenzar a invertir.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Cont&aacute;ctanos<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Si quieres saber m&aacute;s sobre este desarrollo, o est&aacute;s interesado en las &uacute;ltimas unidades de este proyecto, por favor deja tu informaci&oacute;n de contacto debajo. <\\/span><strong>Si eres br&oacute;ker y est&aacute;s interesado en comercializar estas propiedades, tenemos beneficios importantes para ti.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-03-18 10:36:00', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(17, 'how-do-i-choose-the-right-property-to-invest-in-5-tips-you-might-find-useful', 'How do I choose the right property to invest in?  5 tips you might find useful', 1, '01-min-1-400x327_ZzpAODGB.jpg', '\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Unlike choosing aisle or window seats in a flight, <\\/span><strong>investing in property demands a lot of consideration<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> before making the final decision. In this article we have provided some factors you surely have to weigh in before <\\/span><strong>choosing the most suitable property for you.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2397\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/01-min-1-400x327.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"245\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>1. Location:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2398\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/02-location-min-1-400x366.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"275\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This is a key factor. In this regard, you will have to consider the <\\/span><strong>commercial and turstical value of the site<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> you&rsquo;re investing.<\\/span><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Proximity from beaches and touristic landmarks is a plus, as well as if there are any markets nearby, main roads and avenues, if it\'s in front of the ocean or amid the jungle.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Also, you&rsquo;ll have to consider if it\'s close to any possible nuances such as noisy areas or smelly dumpsites.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>2. Accessibility:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2390\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/03-accesibility-400x301.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"226\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Is it hard to get to the place you\'re investing? This is not something you want to ignore.<\\/span><strong> Good accessibility goes a long way<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Dirt roads are no match to paved roads.<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> Is there an airport near your destination? You might also want to investigate other means to get to your future property such as bus lines, boats or ferries.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>3. Low maintenance costs:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2391\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/04-low-maintenance-costs-400x400.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Try to choose properties that aren&rsquo;t expensive to maintain. Keep in mind that <\\/span><strong>more amenities mean a more costly investment<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, although these also add value, but only if well designed and used.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">See if amenities such as a pool, gym, conference room, etc are valued by your tenants and therefore worth being in the project you&rsquo;re willing to invest.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Also, <\\/span><strong>investigate if the material<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">s (roof tiles, gutters, windows, doors, etc) your property is constructed <\\/span><strong>need to be replaced much or have an extensive lifecycle.<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>4. Look for potential:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2394\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/05-look-for-potential-400x225.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"169\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Is there anything valuable meant to be constructed in the next few years<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">? Big infrastructure projects such as new developments, beach clubs, nightclubs, restaurants, commercial buildings, marinas, golf courses etc. All these are <\\/span><strong>likely to make your investment more valuable<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> in the long run.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>5. Research from as many sources as possible<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">:&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2392\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/05-research-min-400x299.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"224\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">This will give you a more global idea about the decision you\'re trying to make. If you only listen or trust the opinion of your broker it will be biased as he is trying to sell something to you.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Check out every competitor available,<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> their prices, the demand of rentals, etc. <\\/span><strong>Speak to locals<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, get a feel of their knowledge, they are likely to provide valuable information such as crime rates, costs of living, taxes, etc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As you can see, there are multiple factors that you have to consider before making such a big investment decision.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Luckily, <\\/span><strong>Tulum has multiple ongoing and future developments that gather these conditions <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">such as a great location &amp; climate, good accessibility, low maintenance costs and lots of potential.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Our<\\/span><strong> 30 years of experience in Neoterre<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> allow us to see that potential in a great opportunity of growth, and that is why<\\/span><strong> we are passionate about developing new projects <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">that will contribute to the foreseeable expansion of Tulum.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you\'re interested in the possibility of investing in Tulum, <\\/span><strong>get in touch with us and we will happily assist you.<\\/strong><\\/p>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-04-13 10:37:48', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(18, 'why-should-i-invest-in-a-sustainable-property', 'Why should I invest in a sustainable property?', 5, '01-650x489_DjUe6ctn.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-2401 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/01-650x489.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"489\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As the new generations are gaining interest in sustainable options for housing, we think investment in real estate should go (and is going) in the same direction.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The following are some reasons why <\\/span><strong>investing in sustainable real estate can be a smart decision<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, not only because of its benefits to preserve the planet&rsquo;s resources, but also because of its <\\/span><strong>potential for profitability.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/span><strong>But first, what exactly is a sustainable property?<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-2402 size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/02.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"532\\\" height=\\\"504\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A sustainable design, for any type of building, refers to traits that help <\\/span><strong>reduce <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">its <\\/span><strong>consumption of energy and natural resources<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> as well as <\\/span><strong>improve the user&rsquo;s quality of life.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Some of these traits include the selection of <\\/span><strong>materials<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> used in construction, <\\/span><strong>use of renewable energy<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> sources, <\\/span><strong>carbon footprint<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, <\\/span><strong>conditioning<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> systems, <\\/span><strong>energy usage<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, <\\/span><strong>water consumption<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, intake of <\\/span><strong>natural daylight,<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> etc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">&nbsp;Many governments have established some <\\/span><strong>standards to certify if a building is sustainable <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">or not. The most known certification is the LEED standard (Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If a construction project makes a smart design that takes advantage of natural light, saves rainwater, has a low carbon footprint, uses quality renewable materials, has natural conditioning systems and is energy efficient, (among other traits) it will likely get a LEED certification.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-2403 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/03-650x366.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"366\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Investing in Sustainable Property<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Now we&rsquo;ll address the opportunities and risks involved in these investments.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The truth is, that a sustainable construction project will be <\\/span><strong>more expensive to build<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, but is <\\/span><strong>expected to pay off in the medium to long term<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, as they have <\\/span><strong>higher rents<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> for tenants.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It is also true that as years go by and ecological agendas are pushed, <\\/span><strong>governments will promote legislation that require more sustainable buildings<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and eventually fine those who don&rsquo;t meet certain sustainable standards. In this sense, <\\/span><strong>investors will be encouraged to put their money in sustainable developments.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-2404 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/04-650x366.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"366\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Evidence shows that sustainable developments benefit from <\\/span><strong>higher cost of rent<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> (tenants pay more), a <\\/span><strong>higher resale value<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and <\\/span><strong>have lower energy bills<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> (as they are more efficient, they save water gas and light). In addition, these developments tend to be <\\/span><strong>more occupied than conventional buildings.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The main challenge for investors is if they can afford to wait for a medium to long period of time until they recover their investment. As we said before, <\\/span><strong>a sustainable development has many high initial costs that aim at setting the ground for being as efficient and sustainable as possible<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. This eventually benefit users since they pay fewer utilities, but also assume a higher rent.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As more millennials start to own or rent property, they will value living in sustainable properties and are willing to pay a higher cost, as they see it as an improvement in quality of life.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>Investing Sustainably with Neoterre<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter wp-image-2405 size-large\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/05-650x496.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"496\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Our <\\/span><strong>30 years of experience<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> made us acquainted with the most ambitious sustainable development projects, so we know the value they have.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We are <\\/span><strong>currently developing many ecological housing projects<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, and always seek for investors. If you are interested in getting in on any of our projects, leave your contact information below and we will reach out.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-04-27 10:41:13', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(19, 'how-to-avoid-real-estate-investment-frauds', 'How to avoid Real Estate Investment Frauds', 1, '01-650x430_THfbr5ZB.png', '\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Are you planning to invest in Real Estate? If so, you must know that i<\\/span><strong>nvestment scams and frauds are pretty common in this business.&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">In the following article, we have provided some guidelines to identify possible scams and fraudulent investment opportunities, as well as strategies to avoid them.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The following are some fraud methods scammers typically use:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>1) <\\/strong><strong>Fake Rental Ads:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">In this situation, scammers hack real property listings with their own data. Sometimes, they even use old rental ads and make them look as new. Once they receive interest from a na&iuml;ve investor and ask them to wire the money, they disappear.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">These types of frauds are always in online-unverified sites, so always do your proper research and rely on known experts, which can help with their opinion.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>2)<\\/strong> <strong>Poorly maintained properties sold as new:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2411\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/01-650x430.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"430\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As a Real Estate investor, you are likely to search for relatively cheap properties in sites with high potential for growth, far away from home. Many scam artists take advantage of this and often<\\/span><strong> lie about the condition of the property they&rsquo;re selling.&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">For example, they advertise the property in mint condition when it&rsquo;s actually falling apart. In addition, they could have fake reports made by phony inspectors supporting their evidence.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">To avoid this fraud, make sure a local and trustworthy party does proper inspections and verifications on the property you&rsquo;re interested in.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">3)<\\/span> <strong>Fake owners:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">In this case, <\\/span><strong>scammers will lure you in buying or investing in a property that isn&rsquo;t owned by them.<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> This is most common in empty land lots or vacant developments.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Once you make a first deposit, the fraud sellers will disappear with your money.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">To avoid this fraud, always verify who actually owns the land or property you want to invest.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">4)<\\/span> <strong>Phony Investment Seminars:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2413\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/cindy-tang-ob-hsLNxYPc-unsplash-650x433.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"433\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">These types of events, hosted by &ldquo;investment gurus&rdquo; are very common, and often demand a high entry price to participate (around $30.000). They often promise secrets for safe investment opportunities with high returns.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Keep in mind, <\\/span><strong>investing is never 100% secure and always involves some degree of risk<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, so be skeptical of individuals who make these types of promises, but most important, avoid these seminars as those who run them will probably rush you into investing in a &ldquo;great opportunity&rdquo;.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Now that you can identify common investment frauds, here are some simple steps you can take to ensure the reliability of your investment.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>1)<\\/strong> <strong>Always get professional assistance:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Do not engage investment opportunities without the help of a lawyer and a professional and registered broker.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>2) <\\/strong><strong>Get everything in writing:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2412\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/04\\/03-650x413.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"413\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Before you spend any of your money, make sure your lawyer settles proper paperwork that requires the selling party to identify themselves.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>3)<\\/strong> <strong>Verify who actually owns the property:&nbsp;<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">And send trusted inspectors to check everything is right.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>4) <\\/strong><strong>Do your proper research<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">As in everything, make sure you are behind the information you gather. Take your time to research as you are probably putting lots of money into your planned investment opportunity.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-size: 14pt;\\\"><strong>About Us:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Neoterre Lifestyle Developers has <\\/span><strong>over 30 years of experience in real estate<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, so we know a thing or two about this business. If you are interested in any further information regarding Real Estate investments, get in touch with our team and we will happily assist you. <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-04-30 10:43:11', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(20, 'what-do-we-mean-when-we-say-by-neoterre', 'What do we mean when we say By Neoterre', 1, '01-650x649_gX0ksJ8K.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2419\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/05\\/01-650x649.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"649\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Neoterre was founded 15 years ago in the state of Yucat&aacute;n and since then has established itself as a<\\/span><strong> top real estate developer<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> in M&eacute;xico, with special focus in <\\/span><strong>Merida and Tulum<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The key to our success was building a multidisciplinary team using <\\/span><strong>experts <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">in <\\/span><strong>construction, architecture and engineering<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, with a solid infrastructure and <\\/span><strong>clear vision <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">of the market.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Our experience has taught us the best methods to <\\/span><strong>deliver high-end developments, with a focus on sustainability<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, using local materials that are prone to have the least possible impact on the environment.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We specialize in residential housings, hotel and subdivisions and carry out an extensive market research to <\\/span><strong>guarantee the best locations<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, satisfy market preferences and needs, and <\\/span><strong>increase the profitability of short and long-term investments.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2420\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/05\\/02-650x866.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"866\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tulum&rsquo;s recent growth has presented a great opportunity for us and our clients. <\\/span><strong>Acquiring a property in Tulum is today an affordable reality, <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">and the prospects of the area&rsquo;s continuous growth are very promising. Plans for a <\\/span><strong>new airport and train<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that will <\\/span><strong>increase the influx of visitors from around the world,<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> are just an example of this.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Investing your assets safely in a <\\/span><strong>stable market<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, with the <\\/span><strong>best quality of life<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> and <\\/span><strong>location<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> while <\\/span><strong>ensuring a higher return on your investment<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> has never been so simple.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">At <\\/span><strong>Neoterre Lifestyle Developers<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, we offer a wide portfolio of interesting developments with <\\/span><strong>flexible financing options.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you&rsquo;re interested in joining our community, <\\/span><strong>contact us <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">and we will be of service.<\\/span><\\/p>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-05-17 17:44:25', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(21, 'why-should-i-invest-in-tulum', 'Why should I invest in Tulum?', 3, '01-650x433_KNA3CcTD.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2424\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/06\\/01-650x433.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"433\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A couple of decades ago, Tulum was just a modest settlement tourists passed by to get to the Mayan Ruins.<\\/span><strong> Now it\'s one of Mexico\'s most visited destinations and is still rapidly growing.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>How and why did this happen?<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The paradise beaches and turquoise sea coasts were always there, just like the incredible jungles and ancient ruins. In that sense, <\\/span><strong>Tulum&rsquo;s potential of becoming the new Caribbean hotspot was always latent.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The saturation of tourists in Cancun, Playa del Carmen and other popular destinations helped attention shift towards Tulum, which has a <\\/span><strong>much lower price per square meter.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Slowly but surely, many real estate developments, hotels, restaurants, nightclubs and beach clubs started to proliferate in the area, establishing a somewhat exclusive circuit that is now ready to receive an increasing demand of international tourists.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2425\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/06\\/02-650x433.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"433\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">However Tulum is just in the way of becoming a top global vacationing destination. Many more developments are in construction, waiting for the world to visit.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>At Neoterre, we develop high-end residential projects in Tulum, <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">ideal for renting and seizing its huge touristic potential. If you are interested in joining our community, contact us and we will be of service.<\\/span><\\/p>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-06-02 10:46:13', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}');
