(22, 'condominium-regime-what-is-it-and-why-do-i-need-one-for-my-property', 'Condominium Regime: What is it and why do I need one for my property?', 3, 'sale-3701777_960_720-650x344_6BEyYZcT.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2433\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/06\\/sale-3701777_960_720-650x344.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"344\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A condominium regime is a public and <\\/span><strong>legal document that sets out the rules and regulations<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that owners of any given property have to abide by, as well as their <\\/span><strong>rights and obligations.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It also <\\/span><strong>describes the specific details of any project,<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> such as building blueprints, location, sizes and delimitations of individual units, percentage of common areas owned by each unit, etc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2434\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/06\\/lotes-nuevo-neoterre-02-650x519.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"519\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">It basically means that you legally own your individual unit as well as a percentage of common areas.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Every Real Estate Developer is responsible for requesting its own condominium regime<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> from local authorities and getting authorization from them in order to do business.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When a development is finished, <\\/span><strong>local authorities grant a certification of its completion<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, allowing developers to commercialize their units.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2435\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/06\\/signature-3113182_960_720-650x433.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"433\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Every individual owner has the responsibility to pay monthly maintenance costs <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">outlined on the regime documents.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">There are many types of regimes according to the characteristics of a certain building: Vertical, horizontal or mixed. For example, on a Vertical condominium you can own up an entire floor (or the amount of space your apartment occupies).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>All existing developments at Neoterre<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, past or present, <\\/span><strong>are under the Mexican Condominium Regime.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you are interested in being part of any of our projects, let us know and we will happily assist you.<\\/span><\\/p>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-06-24 10:52:46', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(23, 'why-should-i-invest-in-tulum-part-2', 'Why should I invest in Tulum? Part 2', 3, 'Feed-Neoterre_06-650x651_EDaQR82U.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2438\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/Feed-Neoterre_06-650x651.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"651\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We recently pointed out in a <\\/span><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/why-should-i-invest-in-tulum\\/\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">previous article<\\/span><\\/a><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, how Tulum&rsquo;s became one of the most demanded vacation destinations around the world. Now we would like to address what the future holds for Tulum, in regards to <\\/span><strong>many ambitious infrastructure projects<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> that are in the making.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The Mexican government knows the town&rsquo;s potential very well and is already making plans to contribute to this ever-growing touristic phenomenon.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>The new airport<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, set to be inaugurated in 2023, is a reflection of the government\'s intention to make the most of Tulum`s treasures. <\\/span><strong>This project will substantially increase the amount of tourists per season.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Furthermore, the <\\/span><strong>Yucatecan peninsula will be more accessible than ever<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> once the <\\/span><strong>1500km &ldquo;Mayan Train&rdquo;<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> is finished. This pioneering railway project will create up to 20,000 new jobs and connect around 20 small towns amid the Mayan Jungle, according to government officials. In this sense, one can expect those towns will be as noticeable as ever, and bring new touristic opportunities to be explored.<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><br \\/><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"><br \\/><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Other <\\/span><strong>notable infrastructure plans like main roads and highways<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> will also improve the quality and value of the area. Dirt roads will be replaced by new solid and lean roads, which will inevitably increase the influx of bus lines and visitors.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Today, <\\/span><strong>Tulum has one of the highest hotel occupancies and is the #1 destination for AirBnB users in the world. <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If it is popular today, imagine the possibilities for growth once these projects are over.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>At Neoterre, we have a series of high-end sustainable developments in Tulum with a huge potential for investment. <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">If you&rsquo;d like to join our community, contact us and we&rsquo;ll reach out.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-07-07 10:53:51', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(24, 'soil-density-the-recipe-for-success-in-construction', 'Soil Density: The recipe for success in construction', 3, 'Feed-Neoterre_11-650x650_aKGzj2go.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2443\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/Feed-Neoterre_11-650x650.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"650\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When handling the construction of any development, there are a huge number of variables to consider before laying the foundations. One of them is <\\/span><strong>soil density<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Are you familiar with this concept?<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Soil density refers to the characteristics of the soil where construction projects are built. This includes <\\/span><strong>compactness, humidity and permeability<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">When selling real estate,<\\/span><strong> one of the variables that determine the lot prices is soil density<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, which has different classifications according to its quality.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">For instance, construction projects with an h4 classification (one of the best), provide a solid ground that allows more available areas to construct (it basically means that these soils can tolerate more weight).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">On the contrary, <\\/span><strong>poorly qualified soils allow fewer areas for construction <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">as they are less stable and resistant to be built on (can you imagine trying to build on quicksand?).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>The best practice to ensure a high ground density is compaction,<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> which is actually one of the first steps in any construction. With appropriate machinery, soil particles are pressed together to reduce air space between them and <\\/span><strong>ensure a solid ground for a successful construction.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>It\'s just a matter of pure physics: a compacted soil is more solid and stable than uncompacted soil as it reduces the entrance of water and air particles.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>Any project that fails to guarantee a solid and compact ground, risks a future collapsing hazard.<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> When the ground is not properly compacted, the soil begins to move and becomes permeable, allowing water to flow in between loose air spaces and slowly deteriorating the soil density.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">In case of an earthquake, a construction with a properly compacted ground and high soil density is more likely to survive.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">At Neoterre, we take soil density seriously and keep an eye on the soil classifications of every project we undertake.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Many of our projects are built on premium h2 and h4 grounds, which allow the possibility of building many kinds of high-quality developments.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-07-15 10:59:25', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}'),
(25, 'tulum-921-5-motivos-para-replicar-el-exito-de-tulum-895', 'TULUM 921: 5 MOTIVOS PARA REPLICAR EL ÉXITO DE TULUM 895', 3, '115995704_156727469345289_1747071971493518771_n-650x797-min_WG84Fo8d.jpg', '\"<p style=\\\"padding-left: 160px;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2489\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/08\\/115995704_156727469345289_1747071971493518771_n-650x797-min.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"797\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A ra&iacute;z del<\\/span><strong> &eacute;xito rotundo de Tulum 895<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, nuestro &uacute;ltimo desarrollo inmobiliario,<\\/span><strong> hemos lanzado Tulum 921<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, un proyecto hermano con la similitud de estar <\\/span><strong>ubicado en la exclusiva zona de Hol&iacute;stika<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, que se distingue en su incremento de metros cuadrados vendibles <\\/span><em><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">(30 lotes de Tulum 895 vs 45 lotes de Tulum 921).<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Antes de entrar en los detalles de este nuevo desarrollo, quisi&eacute;ramos<\\/span><strong> repasar los n&uacute;meros prometedores n&uacute;meros de Tulum 895,<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> que nos hacen confiar en el potencial &eacute;xito que tendr&aacute; Tulum 921:&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">47% de lotes vendidos<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Proyecciones de venta superadas en un 75%<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Incremento del valor del m2 antes de lo previsto (de $250 USD a $280 USD).<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><strong>Caracter&iacute;sticas de Tulum 921:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">45 lotes alumbrados con energ&iacute;a subterr&aacute;nea.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">37 de los 45 lotes dentro de un per&iacute;metro que divide 3 privadas residenciales.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Seguridad 24\\/7 y acceso controlado.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Urbanizaci&oacute;n con banquetas y guarniciones.<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\" aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Ubicado en Hol&iacute;stika<\\/span><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2452\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/08\\/tulum_P&aacute;gina_13-01-650x366.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"366\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A continuaci&oacute;n revisaremos con detenimiento cada uno de los <\\/span><strong>beneficios que presenta Tulum 921<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">, tanto para compradores como inversionistas.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><strong>Precio de m2 por debajo del valor del mercado:<\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Los lotes de Tulum 921 se venden actualmente a tan solo $220 USD por m2, gracias a nuestros precios para &ldquo;Friends &amp; Family&rdquo; dif&iacute;ciles de encontrar en otros desarrollos de la misma envergadura.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Cada uno de ellos puede ser<\\/span><strong> financiado en hasta 12 meses sin intereses.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><strong>El &uacute;nico barrio privado de Tulum con precios competitivos:<\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Encontrar privadas residenciales en Tulum es muy inusual, no suelen abundar este tipo de desarrollos y los pocos que hay venden sus lotes a precios muy excluyentes.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Tulum 921 viene a romper ese paradigma al ser una privada residencial con precios muy por debajo de lo que ofrecen sus competidores.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">De este modo creemos que este desarrollo presenta una oportunidad &uacute;nica para compradores e inversionistas.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><strong>Seguridad las 24\\/7 y acceso controlado<\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">El valor agregado de Tulum 921 es definitivamente su delimitaci&oacute;n dentro de una barda perimetral, que se separa en 3 privadas residenciales: Chechen, Chaca y Polyuc.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Cada una de estas privadas garantiza a sus usuarios vigilancia las 24 horas del d&iacute;a, los 7 d&iacute;as de la semana, y acceso controlado para mayor seguridad.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">El precio al que se venden hoy en d&iacute;a los lotes son realmente inusuales para las caracter&iacute;sticas que brindan.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><strong>Ubicaci&oacute;n privilegiada entre la ciudad y la selva<\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Como dijimos anteriormente, Tulum 921 se encuentra en <\\/span><strong>Hol&iacute;stika, una de las zonas m&aacute;s <\\/strong><strong><em>premium<\\/em><\\/strong><strong> en todo Tulum<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. Este barrio es considerado un santuario para aquellos interesados en la meditaci&oacute;n, bienestar y relajaci&oacute;n. Lo anterior en virtud de contar con una amplia gama de actividades vinculadas al arte y wellness.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Su ubicaci&oacute;n privilegia la conservaci&oacute;n de flora, logrando brindar la sensaci&oacute;n de estar ubicado en medio de la selva Maya. Los residentes lo describen como un <\\/span><strong>lugar ideal para desconectarse y sumergirse en la serenidad que ofrece la naturaleza.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Asimismo, el proyecto est&aacute; a unas<\\/span><strong> pocas cuadras de las avenidas m&aacute;s importantes de Tulum <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">(Av. Tulum y Av. Kukulkan), que cuentan con comercios de todo tipo para abastecer cualquier necesidad.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li style=\\\"list-style-type: none;\\\">\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li aria-level=\\\"1\\\"><strong>Alumbrado con energ&iacute;a subterr&aacute;nea y urbanizado con banquetas<\\/strong><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Al igual que Tulum 895, este nuevo desarrollo se alumbra a partir de<\\/span><strong> energ&iacute;a subterr&aacute;nea, que tiene el beneficio de ser de alta calidad y de bajo consumo.<\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> Es sin duda un beneficio a tener en cuenta a la hora de analizar las boletas de energ&iacute;a.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A su vez, Tulum 921 est&aacute; urbanizado con banquetas y guarniciones para maximizar la comodidad de sus residentes, en una zona t&iacute;picamente constituida por calles de terracer&iacute;a.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><img class=\\\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2448\\\" style=\\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/neoterre.mx\\/blog\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/08\\/daniel-ramirez-tnuZFnY7OWw-unsplash-650x977.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"650\\\" height=\\\"977\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n de rentabilidad:<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><strong>Las ventajas competitivas de Tulum 921 nos permiten estimar que cada lote generar&aacute; un promedio de 90% de rentabilidad en los pr&oacute;ximos 26 meses, <\\/strong><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">partiendo de las referencias reales y actuales del mercado, obtenidas en Tulum 895.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><strong>Los beneficios para brokers incluyen un 6% de comisi&oacute;n + IVA.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">La preventa comenz&oacute; en agosto de 2021 y se espera entregar todas las unidades para julio de 2022.&nbsp;<\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">A medida que se vaya moviendo el mercado iremos compartiendo noticias de ventas de este nuevo proyecto, que representa sin dudas <\\/span><strong>una excelente oportunidad de compra e inversi&oacute;n, en un destino cada vez m&aacute;s atractivo como Tulum.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><strong>Cont&aacute;ctanos<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Si quieres saber m&aacute;s sobre este desarrollo, por favor deja tu informaci&oacute;n de contacto debajo. <\\/span><strong>Si eres br&oacute;ker y est&aacute;s interesado en comercializar estas propiedades, tenemos beneficios importantes para ti.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"ui-sortable-handle\\\" style=\\\"text-align: left; padding-left: 160px;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/div>\"', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'published', '2021-08-06 10:00:48', 2, 'a:3:{s:4:\"user\";s:10:\"neoterremx\";s:2:\"id\";s:1:\"2\";s:5:\"token\";s:128:\"Ax3FjbUV49SY3mdBKeCy4sQYevl1v9MYqiYNuzZpUqu9WaPF9paQktmCHdNKmsz4uNrx2nVltZ2jksJ2UWpo00WjflGl83Urw5FdeVDmfg7UN4feFg8ia5Vto22Mi0a8\";}');

